<h2>Hildegard: Ordo Virtutum</h2>

<dl>
<dt>Hildegard von Bingen (1098-1179)</dt>
<dd>Ordo Virtutum<br>
Sequentia - Benjamin Bagby &amp; Barbara Thornton, dirs<br>
<i>Deutsche Harmonia Mundi (BMG) 05472 77394 2</b></i> [CDx2]<br>
<i>Musical Heritage Society 525505X</i> [CDx2]</dd>
</dl>

<h3>Contents:</h3>
<p><ol>
<strong>Hildegard von Bingen:</strong> Ordo Virtutum<br>
<h4>CD-1</h4>
Ordo Virtutum<br>
<li>Prologue: Qui sunt hi, qui ut nubes?</li>
<li>Processional of embodied souls (instr.)</li>
<li>Scene 1: O nos peregrine sumus</li>
<li>Anima processional (instr.)</li>
<li>Scene 1 (cont'd): O dulcis divinitas</li>
<li>Anima processional (instr.)</li>
<li>Scene 1 (cont'd): O gravis labor</li>
<li>Instrumental dance</li>
<li>Scene 2: Ego Humilitas</li>
<li>Instrumental dance</li>

<h4>CD-2</h4>
Interlude<br>
<li>Symphonia: O quam magnum miraculum</li>
<li>Symphonia: O felix anima</li>
<li>Symphonia: O quam mirabilis</li><br>

Ordo Virtutum<br>
<li>Instrumental lament</li>
<li>Scene 3: Heu! Heu! Nos virtutes plangamus</li>
<li>Scene 4: Que es aut unde venis?</li>
<li>Finale: In principio</li>
</ol></p>

<p>Sources (text editions):<br>
Peter Dronke (Cambridge), copyright 1997
</p>

